<p>Idaho Power offers net metering for solar customers, crediting excess generation at retail rates and allowing unused credits to roll over monthly. While Idaho doesn't currently offer state-specific solar rebates, the state's tax-friendly environment means no additional state taxes on solar installations. For HVAC upgrades, federal tax credits up to \$2,000 are available for high-efficiency heat pumps, while additional rebates may be available through Idaho Power's energy efficiency programs for qualifying equipment upgrades.</p>

